data.description: Welcome home. This lovely home is very warm and inviting. It offers a great layout with a fabulous flow for everyday living and entertaining. Loft functions as the perfect flex space, great for movie nights, workout space, a pool table or whatever hobby you might have. Could also serve as a 4th bedroom or office. Home has been nicely maintained by the sellers. Kitchen is nice and open featuring an air-fryer stove, granite counter tops, island and smart refrigerator. Storage space abounds in this home, including under the staircase.  Extend the entertainment outdoors into the spacious backyard where there is plenty of room for an outdoor kitchen or a pool. Better yet, why not both. Just walking distance to the amenity center. In addition to the amenity center there are plenty of recreational activities nearby, such as Tinman Social. There you can enjoy a vast assortment of dining alternatives, live entertainment, outdoor movie nights, concerts and games. Schedule your tour today!
